Package remixlab.dandelion.branch

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Constants  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GenericFrame
    An interactive-frame is a GrabberFrame that implements the GenericGrabber interface.
    GenericScene
    An interactive-scene is a GrabberScene that implements the GenericGrabber interface.
    HIDAgent
    A MotionAgent<DOF6Action>, such most joystick, supporting Constants.ClickActions, and up to Constants.DOF6Actions actions.
    JoystickAgent
    A MotionAgent<DOF3Action>, such most joystick, supporting Constants.ClickActions, and up to Constants.DOF3Actions actions.
    KeyboardAgent
    The root of all dandelion keyboard agents.
    MotionAgent<A extends Action<Constants.MotionAction>>
    The root of all dandelion motion agents (which may have a wheel), such as a mouse or a touch-screen.
    MultiTouchAgent
    A specialization of remixlab.dandelion.agent.HIDAgent that handles touch surfaces.
    TrackballAgent
    A MotionAgent<DOF1Action>, such as a trackball, supporting Constants.ClickActions, and Constants.DOF1Actions actions.
    WheeledMouseAgent
    A MotionAgent<DOF2Action>, such as most mice, supporting Constants.ClickActions, and up to Constants.DOF2Actions actions.
